## Limitations

This report is limited by the availability of recent and comprehensive data on defensive gun use. The topic is highly debated, and estimates can vary significantly depending on the methodology and biases of the sources. Additionally, the lack of standardized reporting on defensive gun incidents makes it challenging to obtain precise figures. Further research and more robust data collection methods are needed to provide a more definitive answer to the frequency of gun use for self-defense.

